{"tid":839703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾聞 疑月台空隙太窄　高鐵復興號到站無法開門　港鐵：同型車暫停用8號月台","createTime":"2018-09-28T06:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T12:30:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3972856ea0a4afe03f43cf17493a10f52b28095b","tid":839703,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkcnews.com/article/15280/譚文豪-西九龍總站-高鐵-15280/高鐵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F15280%2F%E8%AD%9A%E6%96%87%E8%B1%AA-%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%AB%99-%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5-15280%2F%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa08zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f29e90e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkcnews.com/article/15280/譚文豪-西九龍總站-高鐵-15280/高鐵</a><br />\n<br />\n眾聞<br />\n疑月台空隙太窄　高鐵復興號到站無法開門　港鐵：同型車暫停用8號月台<br />\n撰文: 記者戴晴曦 | 發佈日期: 27.09.18<br />\n<br />\n請支持《眾新聞》，成為訂戶<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪表示，收到高鐵內部消息，一列內地復興號列車於周三（26日）10時45分駛進西九龍站8號月台時，由於月台與列車的空隙太少，導致車門受阻，無法正常打開，最終要轉到其他月台才能開門。港鐵晚上回覆新聞界查詢，表示已發出內部指引，規定所有復興號列車必須使用6號月台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2018/09/高鐵-20180927215510_1dbf_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2018%2F09%2F%E9%AB%98%E9%90%B5-20180927215510_1dbf_small.jpg&h=eacaf59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　一輛內地高鐵復興號列車本周三駛進西九站8號月台後，發現無法正常打開車門。譚文豪提供<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪批評，西九龍站的月台設計理應容許所有型號的高鐵列車進站，質疑事故涉及設計缺陷，或因趕工而粗製濫造，「情況有如訂造衣櫃，造好後卻發現衣櫃太大進不了門口，然而高鐵是千億工程，設計都可以犯下如此低級錯誤，實在荒謬！」<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆查詢稱，26日早上約10時許，一列內地高鐵列車於西九龍站8號月台開啟車門時，其中一道車門未能完全開啟，形容事件沒有影響高鐵營運安全。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指，已向相關政府部門匯報，並正與內地相關單位共同進行詳細調查及測量。港鐵又指，為謹慎起見，已安排同型號列車暫停使用8號月台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請加入成為眾新聞的月費訂戶，長期支持我們的工作。所有訂戶都可以收到我們的「每周時事」通訊 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n月費訂戶網址：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subscribe&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa08zCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=97aa0b70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe</a>"},{"pid":"08e7c732218e60a776951502bc154d6be540f52f","tid":839703,"uid":24730,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"咁基本既嘢都冇度好位，定係早有預謀要重新整過嚟cap水"},{"pid":"72ea3d4e9e1edeec921188e6811aeaa937d896c0","tid":839703,"uid":11082,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"換左成批復興號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea0986ff24a4285814272d04bef8896d0a1b4f9","tid":839703,"uid":15883,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:49:04.000Z","msg":"抄國啲車左抄右抄，邊有標準可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a72865e01565476d5706b95687029bc5df168cb","tid":839703,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n<br />\n埋站唔撞爆月台石屎, 算佢好彩啦"},{"pid":"1aa025293ed94184f77aa6e16a4be7d6b8316ce7","tid":839703,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd73f3689cd77a5dc02429d53899b69cbcf2e78e","tid":839703,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2718268a9342448c7c1718d996a19c9c800afc","tid":839703,"uid":203734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"係咪柒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167b60dda8f795b3dcacc321cfa9d2e43e59f44a","tid"